values: hi dudes. well i dunno y, but i feel slightly depressed currently. certain people have helped me realize that i dont have enough time just to think about life so i end up going nuts every once in a while. when it all comes to the surface. and i'm having a hard time writting songs....which is way depressing. i dont understand. i'm gonna go read my bible...since life is just at a stand still right now. l8r.
hey ya'll, happy easter! we have people over right now...kinda boring. so i'm just chillin in my room. i have a whole lotta of crap i have to do like school and more school. l8r.

Heyhey! another day. seemed to turn out like every other. but then it took a turn..........(if u know me well ask me about it in person). so now i'm super happy and crazy nuts! even though i gots lotsa school, its cool. i gt clean room. later.

Ello urbody. Today was pretty uneventful....it was nice not to have to go to mission for math though! A definite highlight. I stayed home, rearranged my room(it looks so much bigger now) and now my guitar stuff is more accessible. I gtg eat and get to dance. later.

heyhey! today is a good day. Even though it rained...i like it better sunny! well, today i had moms equipped and did sound! yay! haha, then i did math- yada yada yada. so i was on my way to work today and it was cold...the end. haha, i'm bored. I actually didnt go to work, they didnt need me today : ( so i came home and played guitar! yay!

hey! today was sad, cuz caroline didnt come over...cuz shes sick. i still love u caroline. but then work made up for it! work is fun. biology wasnt so fun though. niether was writting, but oh well. haha. lately i've been way too busy! and its horrible to say but my poor guitar must be getting cold. i had youth group tonight, fun fun. i did worship and i'm so excited cuz i'm making a full band with a pianist, 2 vocals, ,guitar and drums! so yea. i'm totally in awe of how God makes everything work!

Heyhey! I'm back from the cruise!..........and i have a headache! anyways, it was fun! i went to the gym alot, ate a lot,swam a little, drank alot(haha jk), played blondey a lot, thats about all. it was kinda uneventful. we got to stop in mexico and see the O'connors for a while. it was nice to get off the ship! Besides that not much is new. And from now on i should just address my  journal to caroline cuz shes the only one who loves me.....

hey ya'll(even though i'm just talking to myself, haha......and caroline)

well today was another nothing.....oh but i'm listening to rock bottom! a classic that i play! nice! ok, back to the day. it sucked, haha. school, work(data entry) the usual. but today i came home and caroline is spending the night! the one highlight of my day.....especially after getting a hair cut from hell!!!! it totally sucks, but hair grows back.....eventually :* (
